{"tid":839524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反對電競入侵球壇 瑞超球迷怒掟手掣落場洩忿","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T09:43:05.000Z","uid":133680,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8aca06fc484266e07ee0df26abc0c4c6a067c64","tid":839524,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180925/58722918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180925%2F58722918&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6972d518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180925%2F58722918&h=3f063174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180925/58722918</a><br />\n<br />\n 電競這項新興運動對體育界的影響似乎越來越大，亦開始出現一些反對聲音，在日前一場瑞士超級聯賽中，就有主場球迷聯同客場球迷抗議電競入侵球壇。<br />\n<br />\n瑞超周一就上演了年青人主場對巴素利的大戰，比賽期間在場的主客球迷就聯手發動示威，抗議兩間球會近年投資在電競運動上，令球隊方面的資源減少。<br />\n<br />\n球迷把大量網球投擲到場內，部份球迷更向球場「怒掟」遊戲機的控掣器，此外又在觀眾席上展示「Fuck eSports」和「eSports are Shit」橫額，並且展開一個巨型的「暫停」符號，呼籲球會停止發展電競運動。<br />\n<br />\n受到球迷抗議影響，球證被逼暫停比賽兩分鐘，讓工作人員入場清理場上的雜物。最終主場的年青人表現未受事件影響，以7:1大炒傳統勁旅巴素利，賽後以七戰全勝繼續排聯賽榜首。"},{"pid":"ab2793afefff3b7924b453976a6e60017e9deb65","tid":839524,"uid":82068,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"電莖撚成鳩日要人認同佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f4faa212f0eaf5c1dba09e5598779a57a48406","tid":839524,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"抗議兩間球會近年投資在電競運動上，令球隊方面的資源減少。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613afc1d48d8e1e6bab0c5a52bd0fd522ac9411c","tid":839524,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"如果